<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA43">
<l>tiṅka ḷitucūṭic cilpalikkeṉ ṟūrtiriyē</l>
<l>leṅkaḷ perumāṉē yeṉṟirantu - poṅkoḷiya</l>
<l>vāṉōr vilakkārēl yāmvilakka vallamē</l>
<l>tāṉē yaṟivāṉ ṟaṉakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Wearing this, the moon, don’t go about asking for a little offering,</l>
<l>o our great lord” thus begging, if the churning shining</l>
<l>celestials do not hinder him, we won’t hinder [him either].</l>
<l>He alone knows about himself.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
